Controllable Car in OpenGL by Jerry Wu

Texture source: http://texturelib.com/Textures/grass/grass/grass_grass_0102_02_crop.jpg

Display Text help: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/20082576/how-to-overlay-text-in-opengl

Lighting and material tutorial: http://www.glprogramming.com/red/chapter05.html


User Interaction Controls
WASD - Move vehicle
Space - Change camera perspective
Arrow keys - Move camera angle
ZX - Zoom in/out
R - Reset
F - Lock speed
